trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.PolylineAnnotation"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation"></xref> path points, which can be accessed using the `GraphicPathPoints` property.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en mängd <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.PolylineAnnotation"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation"> </xref> punkter, som kan nås med hjälp av den `GraphicPathPoints` egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: This collection is used at design time only, and employs serialization to expose the shape of a polyline or polygon annotation, using their respective `GraphicPathPoints` collection properties.
trans-unit.target: Den här samlingen används vid designtillfället endast och använder serialisering exponera formen av en polylinje eller polygon anteckningen med deras respektive `GraphicPathPoints` samlingsegenskaper.

trans-unit.source: At run time, use the `GraphicsPath` property to set the path of a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.PolylineAnnotation> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation>.
trans-unit.target: Vid körning, Använd den `GraphicsPath` egenskapen för att ange sökvägen till en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.PolylineAnnotation>eller <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.PolylineAnnotation>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationPathPointCollection"></xref> class with the specified polyline annotation.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationPathPointCollection"> </xref> klass med angivna polylinje anteckningen.

trans-unit.source: Releases unmanaged and, optionally, managed resources
trans-unit.target: Versioner ohanterad och du kan också hanteras resurser

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref> to release both unmanaged and managed resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>Frisläpp både ohanterade och hanterade resurser. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> att släppa endast resurser som inte hanteras.

trans-unit.source: Forces the invalidation of the chart element.
